Hypothesen, Methoden:
	Communities of different political aspects
		community detection
	Users who only answer, who only ask
		cluster by q/a ratio
	Experts on certain aspects (dictated by own political opinion?)
		normalize tags, cluster by tags
	Most users sign up to ask/answer one question, few make up "the community"
		Plot amount of users that has x answers/questions
		degree distribution
	Wenn nutzer aus einer community in einer anderen community antwortet, wird er downgevotet
	Nutzer finden, die Tag am meisten benutzen, Label Propagation

